import React from "react" import styled from "styled-components" const Title = styled.h3`font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;` const SubTitle = styled.h4`font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;` const Author = styled.span`font-style: italic; col` const Date = styled.span`font-style: italic;` function BlogPost(props){ return(
{props.title} {props.subTitle} {`Posted by ${props.author} on`} {props.date}
) } export default BlogPost
